wikipedia_page.main: Joshua John Francis Earl (born 24 October 1998) is an English professional footballer who plays as a defender for Preston North End.

response: Josh Earl (born 26 June 1981) is an Australian stand-up comedian, television and radio presenter, musician and formerly worked in a school library. He was the presenter of the comeback version of the ABC's musical quiz show Spicks and Specks that ran from 5 February to 19 December 2014.

Among Earl's many comedy performances have been Josh Earl is a Librarian which has been performed in Adelaide and Melbourne, and Josh Earl vs. The Australian Women's Weekly Children's Birthday Cake Book, which toured Victoria and interstate venues.
